    "course_title": "WOMEN'S GLOBAL HEALTH AND HUMAN RIGHTS",
    "description": "A human rights approach to global women's health to provide an overview of health issues within the context of a woman's life cycle. It will pay special attention to the socio-cultural and economic factors that play a role in determining women's access to quality basic health care.",
